## Notes
This project is based on the HDOCKlite docking engine developed by Huang Lab:

http://hdock.phys.hust.edu.cn/

HDOCKlite performs ab initio protein–protein and protein–RNA/DNA docking using a hierarchical scoring algorithm.

---

## Acknowledgements
We acknowledge the developers of HDOCKlite and the Huang Lab for providing the docking framework and scientific foundation.

